            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">What is the difference between a blog post and a landing page?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Blog posts are dated, informational content targeting search intent and building authority. Landing pages are conversion-focused, evergreen assets designed to capture a specific action \u2014 a demo, purchase, or signup. Blog posts often link into landing pages.</p></div></div>
          </div>
